column3: I like the old code slightly better - just add as we go instead of indexing tricks - but if this gives a clear performance gain it's fine with me.\n(if only we could use emplace...)\n
I've rewritten it to use reserve + push_back + back, rather than resize + []. A bit longer, but should be operationally identical.\n
